{"word":"H4445 - מַלְכָּם - Malkâm - mal-kawm' - Malcham","slug":"H4445","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַלְכָּם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Malkâm"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mal-kawm'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Malcham"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>מלכּום מלכּם</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>malkâm milkôm</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>mal-kawm'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Milcom = \"great king\" <ol><li>the god of the Ammonites and Phoenicians to whom some Israelites sacrificed their infants in the valley of Hinnom<ol type='a'><li>also 'Molech'</li></ol><li>a Benjamite, son of Shaharaim by his wife Hodesh</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H4428\">H4428</a> for <a href=\"#/H4432\">H4432</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3230\">H3230</a>, <a href=\"#/H4409\">H4409</a>, <a href=\"#/H4410\">H4410</a>, <a href=\"#/H4427\">H4427</a>, <a href=\"#/H4428\">H4428</a>, <a href=\"#/H4429\">H4429</a>, <a href=\"#/H4432\">H4432</a>, <a href=\"#/H4435\">H4435</a>, <a href=\"#/H4436\">H4436</a>, <a href=\"#/H4438\">H4438</a>, <a href=\"#/H4439\">H4439</a>, <a href=\"#/H4440\">H4440</a>, <a href=\"#/H4441\">H4441</a>, <a href=\"#/H4442\">H4442</a>, <a href=\"#/H4443\">H4443</a>, <a href=\"#/H4444\">H4444</a>, <a href=\"#/H4446\">H4446</a>, <a href=\"#/H4447\">H4447</a>, <a href=\"#/H4467\">H4467</a>, <a href=\"#/H4468\">H4468</a>"}]}